    "\n",
    "Throughout this tutorial, various functions from these libraries will be utilized. In each instance, the application of every function will be explained, accompanied by links to the relevant documentation. Special emphasis is placed on the use of the [Harmonized Data Access (HDA) API](https://help.wekeo.eu/en/articles/9515753-what-is-the-harmonized-data-access-hda-api) provided by WEkEO. This API offers a fully compliant Python 3 client that enables users to search for and download a wide variety of environmental Copernicus products.\n",
