    "## HDA Client Configuration and Credentials Setup\n",
    "\n",
    "# Default location expected by hda package\n",
    "hdarc = Path(Path.home() / '.hdarc')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Create it only if it does not already exists\n",
    "if not hdarc.is_file():\n",
    "    import getpass\n",
    "    USERNAME = input('Enter your username: ')\n",
    "    PASSWORD = getpass.getpass('Enter your password: ')\n",
    "\n",
    "    with open(Path.home() / '.hdarc', 'w') as f:\n",
    "        f.write(f'user:{USERNAME}\\n')\n",
    "        f.write(f'password:{PASSWORD}\\n')\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "4cfbbbca-ed72-46d6-894b-635a09439c5d",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Once the necessary configuration for the access credentials is set, it is required to define a request with the configuration of the data to be downloaded. In this dictionary, the data corresponding to various parameters of the requested data must be specified, such as:\n",
    "\n",
    "* `dataset_id`: The identifier code of the Copernicus product to be accessed.\n",
    "* `startdate` and `enddate`: The start and end dates for the download.\n",
    "* `time`: The hourly frequency of the data.\n",
    "* `variable`: List of variables requested.\n",
    "* `bbox`: The lat/lon boundaries of the study region.\n",
    "* `format`: The data can be downloaded in two different formats commonly used to store geophysical data (grib and netCDF).\n",
    "\n",
    "Since this tutorial proposes two exercises with two different datasets, the following code cell shows a dictionary containing the two requests corresponding to the air quality reanalysis dataset (`CAMS_AQ`) and the emissions data (`CAMS_EM`)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "809c97d1-8bf8-4b76-800c-91a937d39872",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "## Definition of Data Request\n",
    "\n",
    "RequestDict = {'CAMS_AQ' : {'dataset_id': 'EO:ECMWF:DAT:CAMS_GLOBAL_REANALYSIS_EAC4',\n",
    "                            'startdate': StartDate,\n",
    "                            'enddate': EndDate,\n",
    "                            'time': ['12:00'],  \n",
    "                            'variable': ['total_column_carbon_monoxide',\n",
    "                                         'total_column_nitrogen_dioxide',\n",
    "                                         'total_column_nitrogen_monoxide',\n",
    "                                         'total_column_sulphur_dioxide'],\n",
    "                            'bbox': [MinLon, MinLat, MaxLon, MaxLat],\n",
    "                            'format': 'netcdf'},\n",
    "                \n",
    "                'CAMS_EM' : {'dataset_id': 'EO:ECMWF:DAT:CAMS_GLOBAL_REANALYSIS_EAC4',\n",
    "                             'startdate': StartDate,\n",
    "                             'EndDate': EndDate,\n",
    "                             'time': ['12:00'],  \n",
    "                             'variable': [\"total_column_carbon_monoxide\",\n",
    "                                          'total_column_nitrogen_dioxide',\n",
    "                                          \"total_column_nitrogen_monoxide\",\n",
    "                                          'total_column_sulphur_dioxide'],\n",
    "                             'bbox': [MinLon, MinLat, MaxLon, MaxLat],\n",
    "                             'format': 'netcdf'}\n",
    "              }\n",
    "\n",
    "Request = RequestDict[WorkingDataset]\n",
    "display(Request)\n"
   ]
  },
