   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "We can verify that the `Request` variable contains a dictionary with the download configuration parameters that we will use next.\n",
    "\n",
    "Then, we initialize the HDA client by searching for our request using the [search](https://help.wekeo.eu/en/articles/6751608-how-to-use-the-hda-api-in-python) function and downloading the found data using the [download](https://help.wekeo.eu/en/articles/6751608-how-to-use-the-hda-api-in-python) function."
   ]
  },
  {
